Ezeckiel or Ezechiel__27.5__Sea planks: : That is, timber brought by sea to build the city.
Ezeckiel or Ezechiel__27.11__Pygmeans: : That is, strong and valiant men. In Hebrew, Gammadim.
Ezeckiel or Ezechiel__27.16__Chodchod: : It is the Hebrew name for some precious stone; but of what kind in particular interpreters are not agreed.
